# Netlify _redirects file for subdomain routing
# Simple redirects from subdomains to main domain

# Assets redirects - MUST come before page redirects
/background/*      /background/:splat        200
/Cards/*           /Cards/:splat        200

# _astro assets for subdomains
https://demo.adagi0.com/_astro/*      https://adagi0.com/_astro/:splat        200!
https://www.demo.adagi0.com/_astro/*  https://adagi0.com/_astro/:splat        200!
https://demos.adagi0.com/_astro/*     https://adagi0.com/_astro/:splat        200!
https://www.demos.adagi0.com/_astro/* https://adagi0.com/_astro/:splat        200!

# Favicon redirects
