https://demos.adagi0.com/favicon.ico     https://adagi0.com/favicon.svg         301!
https://www.demos.adagi0.com/favicon.ico https://adagi0.com/favicon.svg         301!

https://demo.adagi0.com/favicon.svg      https://adagi0.com/favicon.svg         200!
https://www.demo.adagi0.com/favicon.svg  https://adagi0.com/favicon.svg         200!
